    %b Business Transfers: 
    In the event that Qwiqq enters into any change of control, asset sale, or similar transaction, all data and rights related to the Service, or in the unlikely event that Qwiqq goes out of business or enters bankruptcy, your information, including Personal Information, would be one of the assets that is transferred or acquired by a third party.  %p 
